https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.9.4/python-3.9.4-macosx10.9.pkg : Mac OS 64-bit Intel 10.9 and later

https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.9.4/python-3.9.4-macos11.pkg : Mac OS 64-bit Universal2

